      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I am selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it is a total gem! This car is in stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives just like it did the day I picked it up from the dealership. It\u2019s been garage-kept, pampered, and kept spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new and has been loved every mile of the way, you\u2019ve found it! I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
