    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.2-generation Carrera S is a pinnacle specimen of naturally aspirated precision. At its heart lies the 3.8L DFI flat-six, delivering linear power delivery with zero signs of bore scoring or IMS concerns common in earlier iterations. The 6-speed manual gearbox features short-throw engagement with crisp synchromesh performance, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal power distribution. The chassis is anchored by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), maintaining factory-spec torsional rigidity and impeccable damping characteristics. Every bushing, link, and ball joint remains within original tolerances, ensuring razor-sharp turn-in and minimal unsprung weight. Finished in concours-level paint with a pristine undercarriage, this vehicle represents a turnkey investment for the purist seeking peak mechanical harmony and aerodynamic balance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
